{"tid":1772230,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"公鴨沉迷性愛！「一天十次」戰3母鴨累壞…下體壞死被切掉","createTime":"2019-12-06T12:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T13:28:28.000Z","uid":28114,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"896dca53151439c9b647a21684a4bc47f29432b0","tid":1772230,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T12:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/12/06/2286359-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F12%2F06%2F2286359-XXL.jpg&h=8fb99e5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n英國最近出現一則離奇的新聞，一隻名叫戴夫（Dave）的公鴨，因為和另外三隻母鴨發生「性行為」，卻因為縱慾過度而被感染，主人帶牠到醫院檢查後，發現戴夫的下體出現潰爛的情況，必須要動手術切除，而這項特別的手術也讓獸醫印象深刻。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國《紐約郵報》報導，這起特別的事件發生在英國一座農場，農場主人沃森（Josh Watson）養了群鴨子，其中一隻叫戴夫的公鴨，牠有三個女朋友，分別是朵拉（Dora）、伊迪絲（Edith）、弗雷達（Freda），然而戴夫也因此「累出病」來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/12/06/2286357-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F12%2F06%2F2286357-XXL.jpg&h=66884d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲公鴨被送醫檢查。（圖／翻攝自Highcroft Rabbit, Small Mammal &amp; Exotic Vets臉書）<br />\n<br />\n沃森發現戴夫每天都和女友們交配，即使是在「非交配季節」，每天也都要交配5至10次，不過受傷的主要原因，主人推測應該是在戴夫「求愛」的時候，牠的女友們因為不想要而攻擊戴夫的下體，戴夫也因此付出了代價。<br />\n<br />\n主人檢查後發現，戴夫生殖器末端已經壞死，靠藥物已經無法解決問題，因此將牠送到獸醫院，獸醫索尼婭&middot;邁爾斯（Sonya Miles）表示，戴夫的下體因為過度使用而脫垂感染，如果不治療可能會有生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n最後戴夫的生殖器被切掉，只留下短短一小截，主人表示牠可能會因此感到不安，醫師也說切除生殖器，並不能阻止牠嘗試交配，而主人也說目前已將牠和「女友們」分開住了。（黃韻璇報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/12/06/2286358-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F12%2F06%2F2286358-XXL.jpg&h=141cd232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲公鴨下體被切掉。（圖／翻攝自Highcroft Rabbit, Small Mammal &amp; Exotic Vets臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=648955&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=mainpage&amp;fbclid=iwar0l5kwnql4s7fvhn2taxijdrzky2v8ppkw3up2kduoj8r71g4tlz7cb_g4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D648955%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dmainpage%26fbclid%3Diwar0l5kwnql4s7fvhn2taxijdrzky2v8ppkw3up2kduoj8r71g4tlz7cb_g4&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=c79006be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D648955%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dmainpage%26fbclid%3Diwar0l5kwnql4s7fvhn2taxijdrzky2v8ppkw3up2kduoj8r71g4tlz7cb_g4&h=ec5ab99b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=648955&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=mainpage&amp;fbclid=iwar0l5kwnql4s7fvhn2taxijdrzky2v8ppkw3up2kduoj8r71g4tlz7cb_g4</a>"},{"pid":"efa11119a250b5c0c4a61b6d830e3a40fa5387f5","tid":1772230,"uid":203681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T12:31:40.000Z","msg":"怕.jpg"},{"pid":"4757e27f0f670b5c877939352a2283105210a022","tid":1772230,"uid":28114,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T12:33:11.000Z","msg":"母鴨表示：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/28/104239_3a08963c5b8ec958aeb8a23fd50af1d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2F104239_3a08963c5b8ec958aeb8a23fd50af1d7.jpg&h=493e279a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac26a34b1e597fef44170e314651ed6ac4f9faf3","tid":1772230,"uid":78336,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T12:33:13.000Z","msg":"呢d野真係得英國先有<br />\n係中國壞左J即刻煮黎食算"},{"pid":"4bdbb188cb2251c0b8439447e364bb68aaa22a3a","tid":1772230,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T12:33:22.000Z","msg":"金翅切柒鳥"},{"pid":"351cf92576ca0283ec46561dbe78b7a3503e1b0c","tid":1772230,"uid":110109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4757e27f0f670b5c877939352a2283105210a022","tid":1772230,"uid":28114,"like":11,"dislik